summary:
I have a Bachelor of Science in Biology degree from the University of the Philippines Baguio. I am now transitioning to become a freelancer and I am finding a virtual job for my free time. I have 3 years of experience in the hospital industry and took a freelancing course in Filipino Virtual Assistance Academy. I love helping people with their problems. Always doing everything with heart. My greatest dream is to be able to provide work for those who have low self-confidence. I also want to achieve WORK-LIFE balance. I believe in people and in humanity. 

Let me be a ripple for you and together, we'll make change! #HireAVirtualAssistantToday
